1. On je *vodio* automobil do stanice (He drove the car to the station).
2. Ona je *vodila* konverzaciju sa njim (She was leading the conversation with him).
3. Ona je *vodila* sebe na putovanje (She was taking herself on a trip).
4. On je *vodio* porodicu u restoran (He was taking the family to the restaurant).
5. Oni *vode* sastanke svaki četvrtak (They are holding meetings every Thursday).
6. Ona *vodi* svoju priču na časovima (She is telling her story in class).